org.goldenorb
Interface PartitionProcess

All Known Implementing Classes:
MockPartitionThread, OrbPartitionProcess
public interface PartitionProcess

PartitionProcess is a proxy object used when spawning OrbPartition processes (or MockPartitionThread threads) from OrbPartitionManager.
